title: Chicago VIII (8)
description:
Chicago.  They rule.  Get with it.  If you haven&#039;t heard these albums you haven&#039;t heard true talent.  If you don&#039;t own these albums then you&#039;ve failed ot recognize the brilliance.

This album contains:

Anyway You Want

Brand New Love Affair (Parts I & II)

Never Been in Love Before

Hideaway

&#039;Til We Meet Again

Harry Truman

Oh, Thank You Great Spirit

Long Time No See

Ain&#039;t It Blue

Old Days

Sixth Sense (Rehearsal)

Bright Eyes (Rehearsal)

Satin Doll (Live, 1974)


Wow.  We&#039;ve made it all the way to Chicago&#039;s Greatest Hits.  Coming next, the second decalogue of albums.  How many bands to you know that have 30 albums to their credit?  Not too many...
